Main Features
1. Modify webapp to be dynamic
    - Modify the calendar date to be bigger (Min Size and Max Size)
    - Filter Items should resize accordingly (One Column)
    - When re-sizing the date calendar, if zoomed in, can lead to 2-3 of the last days to be blocked/unavailable to be selected
        - Max-Min 7 items for the calendar date, so no matter what, there will always be 7 items for the calendar date.


2. Availability Tool
    - Allow schedulers to input a specific time that they want to block out for a caregiver
    - if time is already scheduled or blocked, then cancel operation and report that there's a conflict
    - Schedulers should be able to remove an an available time

3. Make the filter side-bar sticky


4. Add Role-Based Access (Meaning profiles for caregivers and schedulers)


5. What the caregivers can do (See in their page)
    - Request PTO
    - Request Change in Schedule/Availability
    - See their current schedules and availability
    - See their 'classes'
    - Update their 'classes' per request to scheduler


6. The filter options should have a clear button to reset all the filters
    - Filter Options should be scrollable and bigger in text size

7. Filter Options should have more sections based on it, so level 1,2,3 and Transportation etcetc.
    - Alphabetical Order

8. Date Calendar
    - Day has to be bigger in size (Monday, Tuesday, etc) [Done]
    - On select a day, shows that day
    - Unselect, shows everything?

9. Add A Profile Page
    - Can Modify email/username
    - Can Modify Password, uses verification through email

10. Login so, if user does not have token, they aren't able to login
    - Token should be 3 hours long (If user already logged in and goes into the website, refreshes the token to 3 hours again)


DYNAMIC NOTES/UPDATES TO BEWARE
1. Classes are going to be dynamic based on the CSV File




